663
00:57:09,920 --> 00:57:13,000
His dad might end up beating him to death.

664
00:57:14,599 --> 00:57:16,119
But what she has done

665
00:57:16,639 --> 00:57:18,840
shows that she is affected.

666
00:57:19,960 --> 00:57:22,840
