00:57:42,159 --> 00:57:44,039
that we are not related,

673
00:57:44,119 --> 00:57:45,679
that I'm not your son.

674
00:57:48,880 --> 00:57:50,280
Don't you ever say that again.

675
00:57:52,920 --> 00:57:55,400
You are our son.

